Haifeng Radio International.

51
00:05:01,900 --> 00:05:05,069
This is the new version of our classic show of Night Talk to Your Heart.

52
00:05:05,069 --> 00:05:07,740
I'm the host A'Yi.

53
00:05:08,390 --> 00:05:10,350
Perhaps our older audience would remember

54
00:05:10,350 --> 00:05:14,999
Night Talk to Your Heart as a loyal friend for their psychological growth.

